{"word":"H4763 - מְרַאֲשָׁה - mᵉraʼăshâh - mer-ah-ash-aw' - Bolster","slug":"H4763","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מְרַאֲשָׁה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>mᵉraʼăshâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mer-ah-ash-aw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Bolster"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05E8;&#x05D0;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05D4; - m<sup>e</sup>ra'a&#x0306;sha&#x0302;h</b> - <i>mer-ah-ash-aw'</i><p/>Formed like <a href=\"#/H4761\">H4761</a>; properly a <i>headpiece</i>, that is, (plural for adverb) <i>at</i> (or <i>as</i>) the <i>head rest</i> (or pillow): - bolster, head, pillow. Compare <a href=\"#/H4772\">H4772</a>."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4761\">H4761</a>, <a href=\"#/H7218\">H7218</a>, <a href=\"#/H7219\">H7219</a>, <a href=\"#/H7220\">H7220</a>, <a href=\"#/H7221\">H7221</a>, <a href=\"#/H7222\">H7222</a>, <a href=\"#/H7223\">H7223</a>, <a href=\"#/H7224\">H7224</a>, <a href=\"#/H7225\">H7225</a>, <a href=\"#/H7226\">H7226</a>"}]}